Class PreferenceCategory

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Preference>

    public class PreferenceCategory
extends PreferenceGroup
    Used to group Preference objects and provide a disabled title above the group.

    Developer Guides

    For information about building a settings UI with Preferences, read the Settings guide.

      • onBindViewHolder

        public void onBindViewHolder(PreferenceViewHolder holder)
        Description copied from class: Preference
        Binds the created View to the data for this Preference.

        This is a good place to grab references to custom Views in the layout and set properties on them.

        Make sure to call through to the superclass's implementation.

        Overrides:
        onBindViewHolder in class Preference
        Parameters:
        holder - The ViewHolder that provides references to the views to fill in. These views will be recycled, so you should not hold a reference to them after this method returns.
